      "name" : "Single Send API Guide ",
      "url" : "https://developers.hubspot.com/docs/guides/api/marketing/emails/single-send-api"
    } ],
    "x-hubspot-introduction" : "The single-send API allows you to send template emails created in the HubSpot marketing email tool using a JSON-formatted POST request."
